            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-20</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed managed Gemini processing for images and
documents.</strong> Files should now process normally instead of failing
before AI analysis with a provider request error.</li>
<li><strong>Improved error guidance for provider request
problems.</strong> When a provider rejects a request format, NameQuick
now explains that updating the app or contacting support is more useful
than changing your template.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
